{"tid":1493773,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"23/8 係我生日","createTime":"2019-08-21T11:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T12:45:15.000Z","uid":71273,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5aa70d5c57d132eefc6d787b3987f53267896d0b","tid":1493773,"uid":71273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T11:12:05.000Z","msg":"後日係我生日，我想要一份生日禮物。<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個月，我哋經歷咗好多，流過血汗流過淚，雖然仲未贏到，但至少我哋喺旺角、金鐘、元朗、黃大仙等唔同嘅地方，搵返真正嘅「屋企人」。<br />\n<br />\n香港係我哋嘅屋企，我相信我哋嘅夢想喺遠方等待我哋齊心去實現。即使面對嘅獨裁政府係幾咁強大，即使前路係幾咁迷茫，即使身體有幾疲累，有你哋同我一齊面對，我就仿似重拾一切嘅勇氣。<br />\n<br />\n我知道呢場仗唔易打，但我相信齊心嘅力量：如果唔係Avengers齊心，Iron Man都冇可能啪嗰下手指；如果唔係齊心，冰島呢個地方都冇可能打入世界杯決賽週。<br />\n<br />\n因此，8月23日，我想有一份呢一世人最靚最難忘嘅生日禮物。我希望香港人可以齊心，一齊組織一條屬於我哋嘅人鏈，開創一個屬於我哋而又自由嘅未來！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DX0ipdB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDX0ipdB.png&h=80712e29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c49b5e32c53a147a3dc683857378bdfe3e53d5ab","tid":1493773,"uid":71273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T11:13:13.000Z","msg":"823 人鏈"},{"pid":"710cb1109d84852f10ef9f6925b99024dfaeeed6","tid":1493773,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T11:13:22.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"846e94af7701026c31925aca7f5f5395ec72f67f","tid":1493773,"uid":71273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T11:13:28.000Z","msg":"823 人鏈"},{"pid":"e44cacdf453f91bc19d94a2c0a52c56c9008c4ee","tid":1493773,"uid":71273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T11:13:41.000Z","msg":"823 人鏈"},{"pid":"adb7c43210d5c47cfc92507284b41135c5870f96","tid":1493773,"uid":191633,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T11:13:53.000Z","msg":"好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定會送到俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f118ee00a827aad74bae034532ce92fc74b40b","tid":1493773,"uid":21336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s